title: [3DS] Puzzle and Dragons + Puzzle and Dragons Super Mario Bros.
description:
Puzzle and Dragons + Puzzle and Dragons Super Mario Bros. Edition for Nintendo 3DS.

Tested flawlessly with Sky3DS and Nintendo 3DS with system version 9.7.0. If you are using a Sky3DS you probably need to update your templates.txt from Sky3DS website to be able to write the game file into your MicroSD card through DiskWriter.

I have not tested this game with Gateway3DS, but it should work fine also.

If you like it, please, seed it!
